thread.title: Late sales spree helps Airbus win 2017 order race

title: Late sales spree helps Airbus win 2017 order race
text:
Late sales spree helps Airbus win 2017 order race 2:37pm GMT - 01:32 
A late sales spree in the closing weeks of 2017 helped Airbus win annual order contest of jets against Boeing for fifth year running. But, as Francis Maguire reports, doubts remain over the future of its flagship A380.
